8 \u0441\u0442\u0440\u0430\u0445\u0430 \u0437\u0430 \u0442\u043e, \u0447\u0442\u043e \u043e\u043d\u0438 \u0442\u0432\u043e\u0440\u0438\u043b\u0438.","spanish":"112. Al\u00e1 propone como par\u00e1bola una ciudad, segura y tranquila, que recib\u00eda abundante sustento de todas partes. Y no agradeci\u00f3 las gracias de Al\u00e1. Al\u00e1, en castigo por su conducta, le dio a gustar la vestidura del hambre y del temor.","french":"112. Et Allah propose en parabole une ville : elle \u00e9tait en s\u00e9curit\u00e9, tranquille; sa part de nourriture lui venait de partout en abondance. Puis elle se montra ingrate aux bienfaits d'Allah. Allah lui fit alors go\u00fbter la violence de la faim et de la peur [en punition] de ce qu'ils faisaient.","spell":"Wadharaballahu matsalaa qaryatan kaanat aaminatan muthma-innatan ya'tiihaa rizquhaa raghadan min kulli makaanin fakafarat bian'umillahi fa-adzaaqahaallahu libaasal juu'i wal khaufi bimaa kaanuu yashna'uun(a)"},{"arabic":"\u0661\u0661\u0663.  \t\u0648\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0642\u064e\u062f\u0652 \u062c\u064e\u0627\u0621\u064e\u0647\u064f\u0645\u0652 \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064c \u0645\u0650\u0646\u0652\u0647\u064f\u0645\u0652 \u0641\u064e\u0643\u064e\u0630\u0651\u064e\u0628\u064f\u0648\u0647\u064f \u0641\u064e\u0623\u064e\u062e\u064e\u0630\u064e\u0647\u064f\u0645\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0652\u0639\u064e\u0630\u064e\u0627\u0628\u064f \u0648\u064e\u0647\u064f\u0645\u0652 \u0638\u064e\u0627\u0644\u0650\u0645\u064f\u0648\u0646\u064e","english":"113.  \tAnd verily, there had come unto them a Messenger (Muhammad SAW) from among themselves, but they denied him, so the torment overtook them while they were Z\u00e2lim\u00fbn (polytheists and wrong-doers).","indonesian":"113. Dan sesungguhnya telah datang kepada mereka seorang rasul dari mereka sendiri, tetapi mereka mendustakannya; karena itu mereka dimusnahkan azab dan mereka adalah orang-orang yang zalim.","japanese":"113. &#12414;&#12383;&#12363;&#12428;&#12425;&#12398;&#382